room_title: Escape room "The Black Rose" by Twisted Exit in Lancaster (CA)
room_description: You and your crew have been captured by Blackbeard, the most notorious pirate to ever sail the Seven Seas. He caught you trying to steal his treasure and has you locked up in the ship's prison to await your punishment. Can you make your way into the Captain's quarters, recover the treasure and escape the ship? You have 60 minutes before pirates return to send you to a watery grave!
